------> 1-Sheep (y=73, x=64, store=630) before breeding with CS 0-Sheep (y=76, x=63, store=640).
------> Sheep Breed = True
------> 1-Sheep (y=73, x=64, store=317.5) after breeding with CS 0-Sheep (y=76, x=63, store=317.5).
_____________ 1-Sheep Mated SUCCESSFULLY with CS 0-Sheep ____________
_______ Breeding=True, Failed breeding=False, Share=False for 1-Sheep __________
